opinions.text:
ORDER
In light of the parties’ stipulations herein, the Family Court’s determination of waywardness is hereby vacated and this case is remanded to the Family Court with directions to enter an order of discharge.

attorneys: Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., Stephen Lichatin III, Sp. Asst. Atty. Gen., for appel-lee.
John A. MacFadyen III, Barbara Hurst, Mary Nagle, Asst. Public Defenders, for appellant.
